				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Am I the only one who read this?  He apparently has a higher level mage on a non pvp server, and used his experience for a little fun on a pvp server.<br><br>Granted I my pvp experience is from lots of arena and duels... however I have no complaints about mages in pvp, as I honestly have no trouble killing basically any class.  Mages have 1 HUGE advantage over any class in pvp.  That advantage our range.  We have the most damaging bolts in the game.  Use them.  Send your pet on the opponent and run far far away from them then shoot bolts while you are out of their melee or casting range.  If they move to you, run or gate away again =P.  Its rather simple and works almost every time. <p><img src="http://shade.austin2600.org/gtt2.jpg"> </a><p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=58324">Shadex Tinkerdink's Magelo.</a></p><i></i></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
