				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">&lt;-- from SZ, 
<br />

<br />
Most pvp that happens is rarely 1 vs 1, it tends to be  a few vs a few or  mass pvp (the most fun). In both situations i tend to find i'm being targeted pretty fast by melles and bards/chanters (as most mages are i find), because we can have pets on 1 mob, nuke a 2nd, HotE on a 3rd, servant on a 4th. 
<br />
This makes us dangerous in mass pvp, sure we don't nuke the most but we can affect alot of targets in less then 12 secs, most other classes tend to focus on 1 target. Whilst we could do 4 targets, generally i would assume (least from my playing) we dont, i only ever target 2 people in mass pvp and pet on 1, debuff/nuke other.
<br />

<br />
Anyhow thats my ramblings from SZ
<br />

<br />
iuar 65 noob mage</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
